本論文永久網址:      Twitter研究生:丁兆蓓研究生(外文):Chao-Pei Ting論文名稱:公共政策之議題管理與公共宣導策略研究-以環保署「少燒紙錢、拜香」為例論文名稱(外文):The Issue Management & Advocacy for “Reduce burns Spirit Money & Joss sticks” Policy of Environment Protection Administration指導教授:倪炎元指導教授(外文):Yen-Yuan Ni學位類別:碩士校院名稱:銘傳大學系所名稱:傳播管理學系碩士在職專班學門:商業及管理學門學類:其他商業及管理學類論文出版年:2012畢業學年度:100語文別:中文論文頁數:101中文關鍵詞:議題管理、公共政策推廣、整合行銷傳播、環保署外文關鍵詞:Integrated Marketing Communication、Environment Protection Administration、Issue Management、Public policy promotion相關次數:

被引用:10點閱:980評分:下載:271書目收藏:2



中文摘要2012年，為了油電雙漲、課證交稅兩項政策議題導致民怨四起，肇因目前許多政府單位，在政策推廣上，常處於由上到下單向推廣，不但與民眾缺乏互動與良好的溝通管道，更容易因政策處理不當而引發危機事件。所以政府其實比企業更需要公關，一個政策從成形到推廣，為民眾所接受，非一朝一夕可達成，政府部門若能有效使用議題管理來框架訊息，透過行銷策略與民眾溝通，並結合年度性的整合宣導策略規畫，將可創造政策的更大曝光量及良好的政策溝通平臺。環保署「少燒紙錢、拜香」公共政策的推廣，就是一個長達七年，並有效使用議題管理及宣導策略的推廣計畫。本研究採用文獻探討及深度訪談法，依據公共政策之議題管理生命週期，從政策初始、議題形成、轉化成社會議題、政策制定及後續效應的相關論述，結合環保署、行銷或顧問公司及媒體記者的深度訪談，本研究發現：公共政策透過議題管理，不但可有效、正確與民眾溝通，並可吸引媒體報導，擴大宣導效應，而公共政策，若結合議題管理與整合行銷的宣導策略，更可延長議題的生命週期，並使用跨媒體之通路主動出擊，補議題管理之不足。本研究將藉由此結果，深入瞭解環保署「少燒紙錢、拜香」的公共政策在議題管理之下，如何結合整合行銷宣導策略，提升其政策有效的溝通、說服及曝光度，以此經驗做為其他公部門推廣公共政策之參考。

AbstractIn 2012, to petrol-electric double up, the stock transaction tax with both cause grievances among the four policy issues, causes many government units, in the policy on the promotion, often one-way promotional is from top to bottom, not only lack of interaction and a good channel of communication with the public, caused due to improper policies to deal with crises more easily. So the Government is actually more important than enterprise PR, from forming to promote a policy, acceptable to the population, reached overnight, government departments can effectively to use issue management to frame messages, communicate with the public through marketing strategies, taking into account the annual consolidated advocacy strategy planning, will create greater exposure to policies and good policy communication platform. The Environmental Protection Department “Reduce burns Spirit Money & Joss sticks” promotion of public policy, is a seven-year, and plans to promote effective use issue management and advocacy strategies.This study based on public policy issues management life cycle , from the initial policy issues formed into social ones , policy development and subsequenteffects of discourses , and combined with EPA , marketing or consultancy firms and depth interviews with media correspondents adopted literature reviews and depth interviews. The study found public policy issues through the management , that not only comunicates with the public efficiently and correctly , but attracts media reports and expands propaganda effects. Relatively , if the public policy is combined with issue management and advocacy strategy integrated marketing , that will extend topics life cycle and use the channel cross-media initiative to make up the lack of issue management .By the result of the study , there’s in-depth understanding of the public policy of EPA , ”Reduce burns Spirit Money & Joss sticks”. Under the management of the issue , how to combine advocacy integrated marketing strategies to elevate its policies and effective communication , persuasion and exposure to other public sectors experience as a reference for the promotion of the public policy.

